highlights.text: Eden Hason has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “לאהוב אותך כל יום” is the highest at #1.
“(It Goes Like) Nanana - Edit” by Peggy Gou is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 83 spots at #62.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 281 weeks straight.
